-- Wendy's company-owned same-store sales off
-- 
-- Fri Jan 4, 2008 8:49am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/01/04/us-wendys-sales-idUSWNAS564420080104

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Wendy's International IncWEN.N said on Friday that sales at its company-owned hamburger restaurants open at least 15 months fell 0.8 percent in the fourth quarter. 

 It said that compares with a 3.1 percent increase during the same quarter a year before. At U.S. franchised locations, same-store sales rose 0.2 percent, compared with a 2.7 percent increase during the same quarter a year earlier. (Reporting by  Nicole Maestri , editing by Gerald E. McCormick)